{"tid":2335591,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"韓團BTOB成員丨26歲鄭鎰勳被爆涉毒多年 用虛擬貨幣購入大麻","createTime":"2020-12-22T04:17:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-22T05:19:36.000Z","uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e010c42887eb4fc02a94e72a022e5630c7fd1219","tid":2335591,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T04:17:19.000Z","msg":"韓國男團BTOB的26歲成員鄭鎰勳，於今年5月以社會服務要員（即公益兵）服役，預計於2020年2月才退伍，不過今日就爆出鄭鎰勳涉毒的醜聞，引起熱議。<br />\n<br />\n疑入伍避風頭<br />\n<br />\n據韓媒《Channel A》率先報道，鄭鎰勳因涉嫌慣性吸毒被警方查獲。報道指：「警方通過犯人的口供及追查賬戶，確認鄭鎰勳從4、5年前到去年為止，與熟人多次吸食大麻，從其毛髮檢測中亦驗出有毒品成分。警方亦表示，已經掌握鄭鎰勳為躲避搜查網，使用網上虛擬貨幣購入大麻的證據。今年7月， 警方將鄭鎰勳移交給了檢方。」但鄭鎰勳卻在警方調查期間宣佈入伍，疑似避風頭，因而惹起爭議。<br />\n<br />\n鄭鎰勳於2012年以七人男團BTOB的一員出道，曾推出《I&rsquo;ll Be Your Man》、《Only one for me》、《Missing You》等人氣歌曲。"},{"pid":"808b4d3a803cf8735e0ba570213aad425153a815","tid":2335591,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T04:17:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201221/XKIDOWRFZ5A6TBQ5LH55RSZRFE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201221%2FXKIDOWRFZ5A6TBQ5LH55RSZRFE%2F&d=YgirQyY3AADlg18%2F%2B2KZ%2Fc0oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=cc98d867\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201221%2FXKIDOWRFZ5A6TBQ5LH55RSZRFE%2F&h=27e2bee2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201221/XKIDOWRFZ5A6TBQ5LH55RSZRFE/</a>"},{"pid":"f4acbb852a0565e57877b9d18d29e263762891e2","tid":2335591,"uid":294121,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T05:13:52.000Z","msg":"Cube隊隊男團都有人出事<br />\n之前仲一路吹奏btob係清泉"},{"pid":"026e7eb19c4e4747a79711be00eaf6172704c2c7","tid":2335591,"uid":127575,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f4acbb852a0565e57877b9d18d29e263762891e2","tid":2335591,"uid":294121,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T05:13:52.000Z","msg":"Cube隊隊男團都有人出事<br />\n之前仲一路吹奏btob係清泉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T05:18:49.000Z","msg":"PENTAGON 食女團<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0e9bddab16f0d547963d4d018ef21edf2f82f04","tid":2335591,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T05:19:36.000Z","msg":"下一個會唔會 (G)-IDLE <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}